00:15:06,480 --> 00:15:08,170
I'll figure this out...

268
00:15:08,170 --> 00:15:10,720
Here, let's try something else.

269
00:15:11,130 --> 00:15:16,140
(laboratory machinery beeps)
(dramatic music)

270
00:15:22,830 --> 00:15:25,520
(heart beat thumps)

271
00:15:26,030 --> 00:15:28,920
I think that might be your
lucky number, Mr. Froom...

272
00:15:28,920 --> 00:15:31,820
You're feeling your
adrenal glands kick in...

273
00:15:31,820 --> 00:15:32,980
Do you like that?

274
00:15:35,240 --> 00:15:37,290
Everything seems normal...

275
00:15:37,290 --> 00:15:39,790
Blood pressure's up a bit...

276
00:15:40,330 --> 00:15:44,500
Hm...looks like you're getting
a stiffy there, Mr. Froom...

277
00:15:44,500 --> 00:15:47,000
I wonder what you're thinking about?

278
00:15:47,380 --> 00:15:48,880
All right...

279
00:15:48,880 --> 00:15:52,550
Let's take things up a
notch or two, why don't we?

280
00:15:52,550 --> 00:15:54,720
(laboratory machinery beeps)
(dramatic music)

281
00:16:00,980 --> 00:16:03,120
