282
00:16:03,400 --> 00:16:06,060
(laboratory machinery beeps)
(dramatic music)

283
00:16:06,060 --> 00:16:08,570
(electricity crackles)
(dramatic music)

284
00:16:08,570 --> 00:16:10,280
Just a bit more...

285
00:16:10,880 --> 00:16:12,540
Stay with me, Mr. Froom...

286
00:16:14,030 --> 00:16:22,080
